{"type": "article", "id": 24292, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-03-23T07:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 1954, "name": "包装"}, {"id": 8334, "name": "yuue"}, {"id": 25261, "name": "ion lucin"}, {"id": 25262, "name": "Squad Ink"}, {"id": 25263, "name": "Nynke Koster"}, {"id": 25264, "name": "Austeja Platukyte"}, {"id": 25265, "name": "Jono Smart"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104502CdUG17ev4aJ3qiD0.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>Elements of time by Nynke Koster</h2>\n<p>这组方凳的纹路来自不同建筑的柱子，设计师 Nynke Koster 将历史上不同时期的建筑饰物翻模，然后用橡胶、木头、泡沫塑料等材料制作。可以看到古典、巴洛克、现代等多个风格，拥有强烈的装饰性和对比，在熟悉之中带有点后现代。将经典建筑风格融入到工业设计中是一个很聪明的办法。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153414TC4OMDfFld7knNJW.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53541667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153414DkZ0eYcTxX5Fpl1M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.25833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153415ulcY6C7FzTshiNSj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55104167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153415phVGHF8c3DAbUgJr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153415UqFocL1J73zutrTR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71354167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>SWALLOW by Austeja Platukyte </h2>\n<p>这张桌子有方便储存的特征，它的四根金属桌腿可以装在木质桌面下，不用的时候就可以把桌腿拆下来收在较小的空间里，这也意味着它容易运输。木桌面的两头有长条形的孔，是用来固定桌布的，长方形的桌布从两边穿进后就是一张干净的餐桌，增加了生活气息。设计者是来自立陶宛的学生，<a href=\"http://www.austejaplatukyte.com/#!project05/cbeq\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153416FOoTDSsbN06EqlR5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.29032258\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061534165wnyZ9WGqoY2JaEN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.84166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153417E1rxIzgL4RBeUwOH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.32166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153417AdromNRxwMWcvnqP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153417eWmDpvwkul85jx2G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>平衡灯2 by yuue</h2>\n<p>这组落地灯来自中国设计团队 yuue，圆形灯头和大理石底座之间是一个类似三角形的结构，灯头所在的铁杆通过弧形的杠杆上下摆动，可以看到天平秤和跷跷板的影子。灯头和杠杆结构也恰成点和线的关系，保持了几何图形的简洁美感。平衡灯 2 是他们之间的升级版，有黑白两款，预计今年上市，<a href=\"http://www.yuue-design.com/works_zh/balancer_zh/\">这里是工作室主页。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061534183J5iV8LTIN1wklX4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153418C1TLvZ297zxI6Rlw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153419oQxcwVlp7mIgA1qU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153419kYsSBhoAlNRHxbd0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153420mtP72IVBLenSkuNb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Simple Shapes by Jono Smart </h2>\n<p>这是一些手工做的陶瓷小件，来自英国的陶瓷艺术家 Jono Smart。他采用了浅棕和深棕两种颜色制作这些花瓶、碗、鸡蛋杯等生活常见的用品，形状简单而没有任何花纹，只是近距离看时可以看到细腻的环形纹路，有温柔的手感。设计师 Helen Osgerby 在 2015 年启动了一个 Simple Shapes 的计划，邀请不同的设计师设计这些手工做的生活小件，<a href=\"http://www.simple-shape.com/shop/\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153420YRI8wUhoGrcbpzqe.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153420awQ5q0hOrAFpiCgD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060615342150dVja3LZorX71AT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060615342119qmEvtSecCDVJ6K.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153422WEJGrltUSa6s072O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>baik by ion lucin</h2>\n<p>这是一款极简自行车，来自西班牙的设计团队想要用最简化的元素和线条设计。从侧面看自行车是黑色的，基本保持了左右对称，像是隐藏在黑暗里。而当自行车开始转动起来时就可看到轮胎和结构内侧橙色和黄色的光，一闪而过却非常绚丽。此外，车架上配有可装太阳镜、耳机、笔记本的小包，也在侧面使用了很亮的橙黄色。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061534221GZKT2lgPx6mnECW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061534225TDQdyCRFJKx8jbh.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66992665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153423WODUKGMyqJFngPAd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66992665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061534231fdVGr5ZusOo8MWH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061534248GYiR0TpnPhvSCu3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62591687\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153424mwxJMt7gAN0RlVS8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61613692\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Seaworthy Vodka by Squad Ink</h2>\n<p>这瓶酒的包装令人想起汽水，包装上不同颜色之间的边缘就像被浪花冲刷的海滩。红色和蓝色是极具张力的对比色，上面用银色泊纸写下了 Seaworthy 和几行诗句，在活泼中带点清新。Seaworthy 原本指能够海运，这几个字的光泽也有点像海滩上的珍珠。然而这款略显清新的包装却是放血腥玛丽这样重口味的鸡尾酒。插画设计来自澳大利亚 Webuyyourkids，<a href=\"http://squadink.com/#/project/seaworthy-vodka/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153424p3R8fcjHxuUhoFwd.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.94375\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153426XJRDviVU3Y58oTPH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.97583643\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153426LMTzPtxnDupyiI2s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.2936803\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061534274CD5fxGRuK2lP3rv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71003717\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153427LF76NpYOUV1ITDji.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73977695\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}